The paper deals with the problem of program reidentification, which is a critical issue in intrusion detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The proposed solution involves the use of a graph neural network, which is a popular technique in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the system behaviors of the program, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and system identification (cs.SI).
